            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tortiglioni</strong> to a pot of boiled water and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked tortiglioni</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and set aside until later</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1664883459112-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
