            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>chopped tomato</strong> with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 100ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [125ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
