          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomato is softened, add your<strong> gochujang paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 30 secs, or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>vegetable stock </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce begins to thicken</p>",
      "order": 5,
